{
  "texts": [
    "x t and h t are the input and output at step t, respectively.",
    "W (i), W (f), W (o), W (c), U (i), U (f), U (o), and U (c) are weight matrices and b i, b f, b o, and b c are bias vectors.",
    "The and σ symbols represent element-wise multiplication and the sigmoid function, respectively.LSTM is a widely used neural network approach in AES task research.",
    "Its capability to capture dependency information from long sequential inputs has made it popular in various NLP tasks.",
    "In the AES task, LSTMs are utilized to capture global context information from essays (Taghipour and Ng 2016; Tay et al. 2018; Ridley et al. 2020 Ridley et al., 2021;; Alikaniotis et al. 2016; Dong and Zhang 2016; Liang et al. 2018; Uto et al. 2020 Uto et al., 2020;; Hussein et al. 2020)."
